metadata.name: Reminiscence
metadata.description:
She was like a beam of sunlight on a cloudy day just like a sunflower, innocent like a lily, lovable like a rose, courageous like an iris, enchanting like the carnations. The tranquility of the sea and magenta balloons were her favourite.

1/1
This artwork was hand-drawn.
Created by Kejedotangin
April 7, 2022

Size: 4320 x 7680
Collector will receive the original PNG file.
